3202   1          //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
3203   1          // Precise formula of Chrage Pump Current depends on DPM, resistor, and band.                   //
3204   1          // If VCO band = 'b00, Icp = (700 * M * 2 * pi) / (778 * 0x01C1[7:5]).                          //
3205   1          // If VCO band = 'b01, Icp = (700 * M * 2 * pi) / (1340 * 0x01C1[7:5]).                         //
3206   1          // If VCO band = 'b10, Icp = (700 * M * 2 * pi) / (1880 * 0x01C1[7:5]).                         //
3207   1          // If VCO band = 'b11, Icp = (700 * M * 2 * pi) / (2340 * 0x01C1[7:5]).                         //
